    <h6 style="background-color:#ffcccb;padding:15px;margin:0; height:45px">
        <marquee behavior="alternate" direction="left" scrollamount="10" style="font-size:20px">We welcome to our Food world <span style="color:green">Taste and Express</span> and our sweet is <span style="color:blue">Milk Made kova</span></marquee>
